data.name: label8.Text
data.value: You'll need this key to reinstall this application, recover passwords or access your passwords from another device. This secret key is not stored anywhere else other than this application and your backup.

data.name: label7.Text
data.value: Your key is used to encrypt and decrypt your passwords. It is literally the key that locks and unlocks your passwords. You should store a copy of this key in a safe place outside of Nuke Nine Password Manager.

data.name: label6.Text
data.value: Generate a new secret key. The new key will replace your existing key. Any passwords or files encryped with the old password will no longer work. Any other applications using your password file will need to be synced if possible or updated with the new secret key and password file.
